  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Number Battle, released in Japan as Sujin Taisen: Number Battles is a puzzle video game developed by Mitchell Corporation for the Nintendo DS handheld video game console. By the end of 2007, Sujin Taisen sold 21,996 copies.\nThe game was later released at the Nintendo DSi's DSiWare digital distribution service on January 28, 2009 under the title Chotto Sujin Taisen (ちょっと数陣タイセン, Chotto Sūjin Taisen).",
